	Position Overview  </p>
<p>
	The Social Media Strategy Director is responsible for the successful development<br />
	and management of digital and social media strategies for client brands and for<br />
	managing / mentoring members of the strategy team.</p>
<p>
	This role requires an innovative and passionate people&#39;s person with prior<br />
	experience of managing and motivating teams of varied experience levels in a<br />
	fast paced environment.</p>
<p>
	The Social Media Strategy Director grasps the big picture of business and<br />
	marketing, and must have a passion for digital trends and innovation - combined<br />
	with a sound understanding of consumers, social networks and brands.</p>
<p>
	Deep experience of the social media world and of word of mouth marketing<br />
	is required, and experience of digital at large is expected. Prior client facing<br />
	experience is a must. Active personal involvement in social media is a plus.</p>
<p>
	Reports to: VP, Strategy &amp; Analytics  </p>
<p>
	Responsibilities overview  </p>
<p>
	The Social Media Strategy Director&rsquo;s primary responsibility is to ensure the<br />
